        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036800
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Oh, I'm sorry, but ever since my husband left, I've been afraid of
          strangers.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036801
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Can you help me? I will pay you if you will find him.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036802
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Calm down, tell me what you know first.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036803
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Okay, so it started before winter.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036804
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I know there was an incident where someone's house was robbed, and
          the first frost was approaching.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036805
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: He told me then that he would take care of it and that no one would
          get hurt.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036806
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Winter came, and there were no bad incidents. Even all the transports
          from the city reached the village.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036807
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I thought he had actually taken care of it until the day he disappeared.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036808
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: He was very upset, saying he had no money and needed it. I almost offered
          him what I had set aside.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036809
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: At that moment, a letter appeared under the door. Hendrik read it,
          then threw it in the fireplace and left the house.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036810
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I managed to pull the letter out. Here it is.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036811
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I don't know anything more. Please, find my husband.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036812
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Please, find my husband.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036813
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: You are my hero! Thank you very much!
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 8189697321039036814
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Thank you for help, I hope gods will watch over you.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
